回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93081562529fe8ef488eabc4014d14a508d45b50","tid":1191394,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例之三毛對答指南：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.）香港人咩都唔做<br />\n答：死港燦咪又係靠中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇中國你地咩都唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.）香港人開始反抗<br />\n答：你班港喱咪又係鳩嗡吓，唔係以為真係可以推倒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.）香港人開街站宣傳反修例<br />\n答：成班毛都未生齊嘅撚樣咪喺度精神勝利法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你以為你地好型呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.）香港人聯署白宮<br />\n答：見到班連登仔以為聯署白宮以為有用喎，收皮啦！好撚柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.）香港人6月9號去遊行<br />\n<br />\n答1：諗住打咭上ig fb刷存在感？死返你個乞衣屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沖涼然後縮入你張碌架床訓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答2：即使比你再嚟多次50萬人行就有用咩？咪又係唱下歌之後第二日照常返工！<br />\n<br />\n答3：今天我/ 要返工不了/做政客嘅爛頭卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 之前連登仔又話焦土？係焦土就咪遊行啦<br />\n<br />\n答4：泛民割席呀！成班柒頭比人利用曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要比人話佢係三毛：<br />\n1.）講真話都比人話係三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.）死柒頭咪係到屈毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.）一有人講異見說話就屈毛，連登仔惡撚過共產黨紅衛兵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3424e4bac0c40c4cc03fe203f61ce4